snippet.textDisplay: I know this might seem evil but man this guy is just too interesting to leave alone. I mean the scientific studies we could get could really help people and to be completely honest, studies have shown it is almost impossible to have a happy life in complete solitary.  I suggest we take a helicopter and tranquilize him and then fly him to a nearby city. We would, of course, need to restrain him but as humanely as possible. We would then try to communicate using either cleverly designing drawings/body language and after we would give him a list to read in every single language that could be closely related. After a proper discussion has been made we can give him different offers and hopefully get to study his behavior and culture or he can choose to go back, but I feel like friendly people will be something he would have missed so I think there is actually a big chance he would take us up on the offer when he realizes we aren't cruel
